      • getVarrays

        @Deprecated
public java.util.List<java.net.URI> getVarrays()
        Deprecated. use getVarrayChanges()
        List containing 0 or 1 virtual arrays. Empty list will unassign the network from its existing virtual array. List with one element will assign the network to the virtual array. This field is maintained for backward compatibility and getVarrayChanges() should be used instead. When used it will override the existing virtual arrays of a network.
